author: itv.com
title: Anti-Trump protesters gather in Cardiff city centre
text:
Credit: ITV News A protest is taking place in Cardiff city centre this evening on the day Parliament debates the state visit of US President Donald Trump.
Credit: ITV News The rally in the Welsh capital is part of protests taking place across the UK. The debate was triggered after an online petition gained nearly two million signatures against the President's visit.
Last updated Mon 20 Feb 2017 Wales South Wales Cardiff
